content.rendered:
Directed by Tejas Prabhaa, Vijay Deoskar

Written by Sanchit Gupta. Priyadarshee Srivastava

Cast Rakul Preet Singh. Sumeet Vyas. Satish Kaushik. Nabin Luhagun. Firoz Chaudhary. Tejas Prabhaa Vijay Deoskar(Police inspector). Sumit Soni(Lafange). Prachi Shah(Nisha Kalra). Rakesh Bedi. Punit Tiwari(Monu). Iamrealmohsin(Chandan). Dolly Ahluwalia. Uday Vir Singh Yadav(Father (credit only)). Shubham Pandey(Couple 2 ( Man 2)). Vikram Sharma (Meenu’s Husband). Pawan Prem Jeetu (as Pawan Prem Patidar)

Languages Hindi

Producers Doris George. Pashan Jal. Salona Bains Joshi. Sonia Kanwar. Eshaan Phadnis. Shivani Saran. Ronnie Screwvala. Maharsh Shah. Sanaya Irani Zohrabi.

Production RSVP.
